<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link293778" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=293778&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F572063-hey-everyone-i-heard-great-things-about%2Fanswers%2F293778-i-m-currently-reading">flag</a>
