<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link544319" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=544319&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F945567-mishima-is-very-clear-that-kiyoaki-is-both%2Fanswers%2F544319-i-don-t-think-he-s">flag</a>
</div>
